channel.title: Bluur Dragon Claws
channel.description:
When I add my dragon claws to my Deltascape V16 client (Bluur based) it comes up as a skeleton hand, they are in a winrar file. I've tried extracting it still don't work though...
How do I fix this?

item.title: Bluur Dragon Claws
item.dc:creator: @raulhenriq raulhenriq
item.description:
@raulhenriq wrote:

Sometimes the ints are not like the ints of your configuration, so you have to take something as example. I suggest the usual dragon claws (if you have then on class8) so you can compare the codes and see whats wrong. The thing is that sometimes it can also glitch other items by adding a new model.

Read full topic

item.description:
@Sinto wrote:

[quote=“lord_fear, post:2, topic:348262”]Have you added the ints to class8.java?
If so, the item model is wrong and you will have to find a new one.[/quote]

Of coarse I have… and yes the model ID is right.
